```python
def insert_after_character(string):
    return string.replace('i', 'iI')

print(insert_after_character('This is an example'))  # ThIs is an example
print(insert_after_character('I like ice cream'))  # II like ice cream
print(insert_after_character('Hello world'))  # Hello world
print(insert_after_character('I'))  # II
```
